    <item>
      <title>伊朗与以色列的一周袭击标志着中东“游戏规则改变者”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和以色列之间长达数十年的影子战争中最激烈的一周之一周五以轻松结束，此前德黑兰宣布击败了以色列无人机对其领土的小规模袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼收购派拉蒙的交易将受到更多监管审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sony-deal-for-paramount-would-draw-added-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿分析师称，收购派拉蒙全球公司（其中包括日本索尼集团公司）的交易预计将受到审查外国买家媒体购买的美国监管机构的审查，以及竞争监管机构的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sony-deal-for-paramount-would-draw-added-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾希望美国和日本接管中国关注的铁路协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-wants-us-japan-to-take-over-rail-deal-eyed-by-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名负责菲律宾货运铁路项目的官员表示，菲律宾货运铁路项目可能会在美国和日本的支持下建设，马尼拉在放弃与中国的融资谈判后正在寻求替代融资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-wants-us-japan-to-take-over-rail-deal-eyed-by-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员调整养老金法案后，哥伦比亚基金经理着眼于 7.5 亿美元的费用富矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/colombian-fund-mangers-eye-750-million-bonanza-as-senators-tweak-pension-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚立法者在国会的养老金法案中添加了一项条款，允许基金经理额外收取 7.5 亿美元的管理费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/colombian-fund-mangers-eye-750-million-bonanza-as-senators-tweak-pension-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 21:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
