    <item>
      <title>麦克勒姆认为加拿大预算对财政轨道影响不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/macklem-sees-little-impact-of-canada-budget-on-fiscal-track</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂夫·麦克勒姆 (Tiff Macklem) 建议总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 最近的预算——这抵消了资本利得税上调和更高的收入预测带来的巨额支出增长——并没有实质性增加通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/macklem-sees-little-impact-of-canada-budget-on-fiscal-track</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:33:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥夫拉多尔在其大型项目中动用了陆军，而墨西哥的不安全局势却在恶化 (1)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/amlo-usa-al-ejercito-en-sus-megaproyectos-y-la-inseguridad-en-mexico-se-agudiza-lv5q6l8j</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔委托武装部队建设基础设施并保障公共安全。他的任期将以新建的交通枢纽、酒店和博物馆以及超过 170,000 起谋杀案结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/amlo-usa-al-ejercito-en-sus-megaproyectos-y-la-inseguridad-en-mexico-se-agudiza-lv5q6l8j</guid>
